Roadmap to version > 1.0:

Functionality to add:
    Many more commands - egen, input, label
    Statement grouping / blocks
    Loops - foreach, while, forvalues
    Formats
    
    Graphics?

    A mechanism for registering an arbitrary R function obeying the
    calling convention as a Stata command

Things the grammar should support
    blocks

    loops - foreach, while, forvalues

    datetime literals
    datelists
    real general varlists: factors, interactions, etc
    numlists
    abbreviations for commands and other keywords (+ the * glob syntax)
    
    macros...

